### TITLE ###
String plus int shows migration hint
### INPUT ###
x = "count: " + 5
### STDERR ###
error[RAD30002]: Invalid operand types: cannot do 'str + int'
  --> <script>:1:5
  |
1 | x = "count: " + 5
  | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  |
   = help: In v0.9, + no longer coerces types. Use string interpolation instead. See: https://amterp.github.io/rad/migrations/v0.9/
   = info: rad explain RAD30002

### EXIT ###
1
